{
  "stem": "12402.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He took me home-- and I was so dirty from the-- from the smoke from the train.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, it was so dirty.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he gave me meals and he-- and while we-- while being day, rolls out the couch-- you know, there was like a hide-a-bed.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was not a bed, it was a-- like a-- like an open space, he rolls it out, saying this is all yours.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You take it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You're gonna need it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, you know, the man, he was-- he was joyous.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was so happy, you know, to see me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he tells me, you know, I wouldn't-- I wouldn't advise you to stay here.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And one day comes-- I forgot the story, but he hid me in the attic.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That was the story in the paper, the attic.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He kept me in the attic.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And next door, when I with him the first time, the next-- next-- not far from him, a woman, Jewish boy went in to pick up laundry or something, and they-- they founded a boy, a Jewish boy was there.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They took out the woman.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They shot her right away on the spot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what-- what this Wenzel said, don't stay here, and that time it happened that where they murdered 23 Jews in t you know, that was after the war.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, it's very dangerous.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They're killing Jews left and right-- not-- not the German, the Polish people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I suggest you should leave as soon as you can.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So all right, I took the train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I took the shoes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went to Warsaw, and I went to the flea market, and they were selling the Jews-- the-- not the-- There was Jews already there, and I sold the shoes.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
